conformanceStatements.description: If RXA-20 is valued 'CP' or 'PA' and the first occurrence of RXA-9.1 is valued '00' and RXA-5.1 is valued with a CVX code from table PHVS_VISVaccines_IIS (See Appendix A) then for each vaccine information statement that was shared there SHALL be:[one OBX segment with OBX-3.1 valued '69764-9' (bar coded) and one OBX with OBX-3.1 valued '29769-7' (presentation or delivery date) associated. Both OBX shall have the same value in OBX-4] OR[one OBX segment with OBX-3.1 valued '30956-7' (vaccine type) and one OBX segment with OBX-3.1 valued '29768-9' (version date) and one OBX with OBX-3.1 valued '29769-7' (presentation or delivery date) associated. All three OBX shall have the same value in OBX-4]
conformanceStatements.assertion:
<Assertion xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
            <IMPLY>
              <AND>
                <AND>
                  <OR>
                    <PlainText IgnoreCase="false" Path="3[1].20[1]" Text="CP"/>
                    <PlainText IgnoreCase="false" Path="3[1].20[1]" Text="PA"/>
                  </OR>
                  <PlainText IgnoreCase="false" Path="3[1].9[1].1[1]" Text="00"/>
                </AND>
                <ValueSet BindingLocation="1" BindingStrength="R" Path="3[1].5[1].1[1]" ValueSetID="PHVS_VISVaccines_IIS_6"/>
              </AND>
              <Plugin QualifiedClassName="gov.nist.healthcare.hl7.v2.iz.plugins.IZ24Constraint"/>
            </IMPLY>
          </Assertion>

conformanceStatements.description: If RXA-20 is valued 'CP' or 'PA' and the first occurrence of RXA-9.1 (Administration Note.code) is '00' then the message SHALL include an OBX segment associated with the RXA with OBX-3.1 shall equal '64994-7'
conformanceStatements.assertion:
<Assertion xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
            <IMPLY>
              <AND>
                <AND>
                  <Presence Path="3[1].9[1].1[1]"/>
                  <PlainText IgnoreCase="false" Path="3[1].9[1].1[1]" Text="00"/>
                </AND>
                <AND>
                  <Presence Path="3[1].20[1]"/>
                  <StringList CSV="CP,PA" Path="3[1].20[1]"/>
                </AND>
              </AND>
              <AND>
                <Presence Path="5[1]"/>
                <PlainText AtLeastOnce="true" IgnoreCase="false" Path="5[*].1[1].3[1].1[1]" Text="64994-7"/>
              </AND>
            </IMPLY>
          </Assertion>

                <Presence Path="20[1]"/>

              </AND>

          </Assertion>

          </Assertion>
